## Report Type: **[L] Large Group Reservation**
### Fields to be included in the report:
User name
User phone
User email
Party size
Requested date
Requested time
Amount of days
Special requests
40-word summary

### Subject line format:
Congratulations with a LARGE GROUP RESERVATION! [user name] [user phone] [12-word additional summary]

### SMS example:
Congratulations! LARGE GROUP RESERVATION: [user name] [user phone] [20-word additional summary] Truly, [agent name], [agent title]

